{"tid":660983,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"台電499之亂","createTime":"2018-05-11T07:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T07:12:55.000Z","uid":5134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"56b4f124060c5f850a9da4d3d34f2e2d254214fc","tid":660983,"uid":5134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:00:50.000Z","msg":"電信三雄紛紛推出 499 4G 上網吃到飽方案，造成民眾大排長龍搶購；這個方案本身毫無疑問地非常有競爭力，但如果仔細考慮違約金、購機補貼，甚至想想你是否真的需要吃到飽，就會發現或許還有更划算的選擇，不必真的一窩蜂跑去排 499 方案。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/145406_5d2fcbebb0664e8cb32e8ad19057e5b9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F145406_5d2fcbebb0664e8cb32e8ad19057e5b9.png&h=8fc51d04&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/145407_cbd0b90f220675dcd810208cd108bd89.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F145407_cbd0b90f220675dcd810208cd108bd89.png&h=1eb3dc41&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/145408_1ab9618da69bafc2349243bf3452b458.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F145408_1ab9618da69bafc2349243bf3452b458.png&h=a94611b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/145658_8deab8a0f09eba1776df96b4c735842f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F145658_8deab8a0f09eba1776df96b4c735842f.png&h=3860ac35&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/145704_965bf20a52e14fa97e6a911db2150bab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F145704_965bf20a52e14fa97e6a911db2150bab.png&h=e65a4e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n百幾蚊一個4G任用不限速就暴動咁制了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n